        "TileImage": "$($repository 6b5d5e16-8f8a-4e39-a424-19b4f981e927).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. The Global Inovation Race has contracted us to eliminate 5 suspects this afternoon. A fecal swastika was discovered in the race track garage basement lavatory and the ensuing Twitter &quot;shitstorm&quot; has convinced management to simply do away with anyone who was seen entering the bathroom on security camera footage. They ask us to utilize a series of accidents to avoid direct implication, 47.",
